{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Some 17 years ago, I became allergic to Delhi's air."},{"time":5000,"text":"My doctors told me that my lung capacity"},{"time":8000,"text":"had gone down to 70 percent,"},{"time":10000,"text":"and it was killing me."},{"time":11000,"text":"With the help of IIT,"},{"time":14000,"text":"TERI, and learnings from NASA,"},{"time":16000,"text":"we discovered that there are three"},{"time":19000,"text":"basic green plants,"},{"time":21000,"text":"common green plants, with which"},{"time":23000,"text":"we can grow all the fresh air"},{"time":24000,"text":"we need indoors to keep us healthy."},{"time":27000,"text":"We've also found that you can"},{"time":29000,"text":"reduce the fresh air requirements"},{"time":31000,"text":"into the building, while maintaining"},{"time":33000,"text":"industry indoor air-quality standards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36000,"text":"The three plants are Areca palm,"},{"time":38000,"text":"Mother-in-Law's Tongue and money plant."},{"time":42000,"text":"The botanical names are in front of you."},{"time":46000,"text":"Areca palm is a plant which"},{"time":48000,"text":"removes CO2 and converts it into oxygen."},{"time":52000,"text":"We need four shoulder-high plants per person,"},{"time":56000,"text":"and in terms of plant care,"},{"time":58000,"text":"we need to wipe the leaves"},{"time":59000,"text":"every day in Delhi, and perhaps"},{"time":61000,"text":"once a week in cleaner-air cities."},{"time":63000,"text":"We had to grow them in vermi manure,"},{"time":66000,"text":"which is sterile, or hydroponics,"},{"time":69000,"text":"and take them outdoors every three to four months."},{"time":73000,"text":"The second plant is Mother-in-law's Tongue,"},{"time":76000,"text":"which is again a very common plant,"},{"time":78000,"text":"and we call it a bedroom plant,"},{"time":80000,"text":"because it converts CO2 into oxygen at night."},{"time":83000,"text":"And we need six to eight waist-high plants per person."},{"time":88000,"text":"The third plant is money plant,"},{"time":90000,"text":"and this is again a very common plant;"},{"time":93000,"text":"preferably grows in hydroponics."},{"time":96000,"text":"And this particular plant removes formaldehydes"},{"time":99000,"text":"and other volatile chemicals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100000,"text":"With these three plants,"},{"time":102000,"text":"you can grow all the fresh air you need."},{"time":104000,"text":"In fact, you could be in a bottle"},{"time":106000,"text":"with a cap on top, and you would not die at all,"},{"time":110000,"text":"and you would not need any fresh air."},{"time":113000,"text":"We have tried these plants at our"},{"time":115000,"text":"own building in Delhi, which is a"},{"time":118000,"text":"50,000-square-feet, 20-year-old building."},{"time":121000,"text":"And it has close to 1,200 such plants for 300 occupants."},{"time":125000,"text":"Our studies have found that there is"},{"time":127000,"text":"a 42 percent probability of one's blood oxygen"},{"time":131000,"text":"going up by one percent if one stays indoors"},{"time":133000,"text":"in this building for 10 hours."},{"time":136000,"text":"The government of India has discovered"},{"time":139000,"text":"or published a study to show"},{"time":141000,"text":"that this is the healthiest building in New Delhi."},{"time":144000,"text":"And the study showed that,"},{"time":147000,"text":"compared to other buildings,"},{"time":148000,"text":"there is a reduced incidence of"},{"time":150000,"text":"eye irritation by 52 percent,"},{"time":152000,"text":"respiratory systems by 34 percent,"},{"time":156000,"text":"headaches by 24 percent,"},{"time":157000,"text":"lung impairment by 12 percent and asthma by nine percent."},{"time":161000,"text":"And this study has been published on September 8, 2008,"},{"time":165000,"text":"and it's available on the government of India website."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168000,"text":"Our experience points to an"},{"time":170000,"text":"amazing increase in human productivity"},{"time":174000,"text":"by over 20 percent by using these plants."},{"time":177000,"text":"And also a reduction in energy requirements in buildings"},{"time":181000,"text":"by an outstanding 15 percent, because you need less fresh air."},{"time":187000,"text":"We are now replicating this in a"},{"time":188000,"text":"1.75-million-square-feet building,"},{"time":191000,"text":"which will have 60,000 indoor plants."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"Why is this important?"},{"time":195000,"text":"It is also important for the environment,"},{"time":197000,"text":"because the world's energy"},{"time":198000,"text":"requirements are expected to grow"},{"time":200000,"text":"by 30 percent in the next decade."},{"time":202000,"text":"40 percent of the world's energy is taken"},{"time":203000,"text":"up by buildings currently,"},{"time":205000,"text":"and 60 percent of the world's population"},{"time":207000,"text":"will be living in buildings in cities"},{"time":210000,"text":"with a population of over one million in the next 15 years."},{"time":214000,"text":"And there is a growing preference for living"},{"time":216000,"text":"and working in air-conditioned places."},{"time":220000,"text":"\"Be the change you want to see in the world,\""},{"time":222000,"text":"said Mahatma Gandhi."},{"time":223000,"text":"And thank you for listening."},{"time":224000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}